        <p class="subtitle">Scholarly &amp; Cultural Contributions</p>

        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="card-tag">Key Outcomes</div>
          <div class="key-list">
            <div class="key-item">
              <div class="key-icon">✦</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Poetic Fragmentation &amp; Memory</h3>
                <p>
                  Clarify how Kaur’s fragmented poetics enact the psychological
                  experience of traumatic memory.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="key-item">
              <div class="key-icon">☉</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Symbolic Expression of Repression</h3>
