                  Show how metaphors and recurring images render repressed
                  trauma visible.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="key-item">
              <div class="key-icon">⌘</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Destabilised Identity &amp; Lacanian Reading</h3>
                <p>
                  Demonstrate how the collection illuminates fractured subjectivity
                  within the symbolic order.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="key-item">
              <div class="key-icon">♀</div>
              <div>
                <h3>Feminist Significance</h3>
